        <content><![CDATA[<p>It's also possible to have different sites for each language. To share content between sites, it must be placed in the <code>/shared/</code> folder under the root site. With this option, it's possible to have similar approaches as described in sections <a href="%(link0)">"Independent subsites"</a> and&nbsp;<a href="%(link1)">"Sibling subsites"</a>. Just set the <code>locale</code> property accordingly at each site's root folder.</p>]]></content>
